snippet.title: Aquaman 2 (Hopefully) No More?? | Johnny Depp Takes Action Against Amber Heard |When #MeToo Fails..
snippet.description:
Aquaman star Amber heard has long been accusing Johnny Depp of domestic abuse. But was the new evidence that we've seen, it looks more like Johnny Depp was the one that was truly the victim in this circumstance. Let me know what you think, and below are some links if you need help. 

If you are in an abusive relationship, make sure you reach out, someone will be able to help you. There are agencies and shelters in place for victims of domestic abuse, you are not alone.

https://www.domesticshelters.org/help#?page=1

https://ncadv.org/get-help
